OL,4,CSalman Rushdie lost sight in one eye,
OL,5,Cagent says
OL,6, Author Salman Rushdie has lost vision
OL,7, in one eye and the use of one hand
OL,8, following his stabbing in New York in
OL,9, August, his agent says.
OL,11,F"He has about 15 more wounds in his
OL,12,Fchest," Andrew Wylie, a New York-based
OL,13,Fagent, also told Spain's El Pais
OL,14,Fnewspaper. "It was a a brutal attack."
OL,16,FMr Wylie said he could not disclose the
OL,17,Fnovelist's whereabouts. The assault
OL,18,Foccurred at an event in New York state.
OL,20,FMr Rushdie has long faced death threats
OL,21,Ffor his 1988 novel The Satanic Verses.
